Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.87,0:00:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So we meet at last, Ayato Amagiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.84,0:00:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have been looking forward to this day!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.63,0:00:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As I'm always hearing\Nabout you from my master,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.47,0:00:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I expect great things of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.85,0:00:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please trigger more exhilaration\Nin me than Kirin Toudou did!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.82,0:00:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately,\NI can't guarantee that I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.86,0:00:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But this match...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.45,0:00:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Victory will be ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.45,0:00:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.67,0:00:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.87,0:00:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All I have to do now is pray\Nthat you two are worthy of my respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.88,0:00:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You good-for-nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.72,0:00:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your body is inefficient enough as it is,\Nso ease up on the inane chatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.43,0:01:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, I'll make sure you never\Nopen that mouth of yours again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.19,0:01:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But clearly, you're speaking\Nfar more than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.52,0:01:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, I don't have\Nthe type of mouth that opens.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.11,0:01:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to stop trying\Nto get in the last word, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.99,0:01:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How bizarre are those two puppets?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.45,0:01:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, I'm a little glad\Nthat we're facing them in the finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.83,0:01:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because now we can attack them\Nwithout holding back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.09,0:01:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, as far as being worthy opponents,\NI suppose you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.80,0:01:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Looks like Amagiri's not going to\Nuse the Ser=Versta in this match, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.77,0:01:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think the phrase\Nyou're looking for here is "can't use it."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.44,0:01:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}According to one rumor, he's applied\Nfor an emergency freezing process.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.74,0:01:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, everyone knows\Nhow difficult the Ser=Versta can be.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.03,0:02:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There might have been some trouble\Nwe don't know about.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.33,0:02:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,During the semifinal,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.20,0:02:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,all I thought was that he'd sent it in\Nfor maintenance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.79,0:02:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have a souvenir for you to take home.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.50,0:02:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You can decide after seeing it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.75,0:02:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But really...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.76,0:02:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What a tacky souvenir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.77,0:03:55.32,ArcName,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Phoenix Showdown
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.06,0:03:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}All right, everybody!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.11,0:03:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Like it or not, this is the very last match\Nof the Phoenix Festa!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.19,0:04:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Now, who will be the ones\Nto reach the top?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Phoenix Festa Final Match!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.24,0:04:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Battle...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...start!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.79,0:04:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Let's go, Julis!\N- Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, my! What's up with this move\Nby the Amagiri/Riessfeld team?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.80,0:04:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Looks like they're joining forces\Nto crush AR-D together, right at the outset.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.77,0:04:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Amagiri Shinmei Style,\NSecond Sword...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nine-fanged Sword!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.74,0:04:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad, but I already have\Nthe data on that move!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.54,0:04:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thought you would!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Primrose!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.84,0:04:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Amagiri Shinmei Style...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.97,0:05:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You must be quite confident\Nto leave me by the wayside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.85,0:05:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're keeping an eye on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.43,0:05:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So assuming we're gonna\Ngo after AR-D together...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.73,0:05:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}what are we going to do\Nabout RM-C in the meantime?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.98,0:05:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're going to use\Nyour state of Vijñāna.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}True, if I use that, I can get a good read\Non what's going on in the whole arena.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.41,0:05:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You can grasp RM-C's and my\Nmovements simultaneously, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.67,0:05:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Julis!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.09,0:05:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We can reduce the risks of fighting\Ntwo against one by a lot now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.09,0:05:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C-Can you believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.30,0:05:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.10,0:05:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That evasion just now...\NAmagiri was guiding Riessfeld!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.02,0:05:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm just guessing here,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.56,0:06:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but Amagiri must be predicting\NRM-C's every move!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.69,0:06:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Burst into bloom...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.70,0:06:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Livingstone Daisy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.11,0:06:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato, I'm going to bombard him now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.24,0:06:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.63,0:06:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about time-consuming...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.59,0:06:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Amagiri Shinmei Style,\NSecond Sword...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.01,0:06:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ten Linked Thistles!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.97,0:06:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.28,0:06:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the moment\NI've been waiting for!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.61,0:06:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come out...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.91,0:06:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gloriosa!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.37,0:06:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.92,0:07:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe that armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.76,0:07:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we'll have to regroup for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Still, they're not going to fall\Nfor the same trick twice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.72,0:07:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad we couldn't take him out\Nwith that attack just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.27,0:07:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If only I had the Ser=Versta...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.56,0:07:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.94,0:07:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Their strategy was to attack me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.11,0:07:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,in order to draw\Nyour protective barrier away?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.86,0:07:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.03,0:07:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that whole series of moves\Nwas all part of their strategy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.78,0:07:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But apparently this fool's armor\Nwas more durable than they'd imagined.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.63,0:07:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was splendid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.84,0:07:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What a splendid combination,\NAyato Amagiri
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and Julis-Alexia von Riessfeld!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.55,0:07:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, more than\Nthe day before yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.76,0:07:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Today, more than yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:08:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Without question, we've evolved!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.52,0:08:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But apparently,\Nyou two have surpassed even us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.52,0:08:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then we have to unveil\Nour secret technique sooner!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.82,0:08:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There it is, there it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.70,0:08:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AR-D's announcement!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.03,0:08:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean that we'll be\Nseeing that fusion again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.92,0:08:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd intended to do so from the start,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.38,0:08:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but as usual, you vetoed me, RM-C.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.01,0:08:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.76,0:08:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, our master told us\Nnot to use it lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.47,0:08:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But in order to defeat you two for sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.77,0:08:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,there doesn't seem\Nto be any other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.65,0:08:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That fusion thing of yours\Ntakes forever to prepare.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.52,0:08:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And we're not going to miss our chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.28,0:08:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think our master wouldn't\Nhave a countermeasure in place?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.03,0:08:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ruin-Sharif...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.04,0:09:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mode: Wolkenwurf...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.13,0:09:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, you're not!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.96,0:09:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maximum...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.30,0:09:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Julis! Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.56,0:09:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, RM-C!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.81,0:09:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}ACM Unit, First External Armor,\Npurging all Luxes...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.03,0:09:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ceding Limit Control.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There they are, there they are,\Nthere they are! Oh, yes, they're here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.13,0:09:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Start linking!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.89,0:10:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now that it's come to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.43,0:10:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Amagiri just charged in,\Nrisking certain damage!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.90,0:10:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, he's desperate\Nto stop the fusion, after all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How unfortunate for you,\NAyato Amagiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.24,0:10:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Camilla Pareto... Badge broken!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.62,0:10:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you were a step too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.21,0:10:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fusion complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.38,0:10:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'm leaving the rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.84,0:10:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.60,0:10:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, why don't we\Nget Round 2 started?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.24,0:10:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saya...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.97,0:11:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saya, let me go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.57,0:11:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flora!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't come near!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.49,0:11:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to rescue you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.67,0:12:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}First the Shadows\Nfrom the first floor, and now this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.97,0:12:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It must be someone with the ability\Nto weaponize Shadows.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.93,0:12:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Meaning that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.64,0:12:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This location is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.60,0:12:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the optimal place for this person\Nto use those powers to the max, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.83,0:12:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.38,0:12:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kirin Toudou, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.34,0:12:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So they sent in one of their big guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.71,0:12:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the kidnapper?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.05,0:12:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please, that's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.51,0:12:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you get in my way,\Nthis girl's life will be in the balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.72,0:12:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It'll only put you at a disadvantage\Nif you do such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.65,0:12:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then go ahead and give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.73,0:12:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But let me advise you of one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.19,0:13:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As far as my own welfare is concerned,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.15,0:13:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that doesn't concern me in the least.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.74,0:13:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,First, toss away your weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.12,0:13:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kirin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.42,0:13:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This sniper... Saya Sasamiya, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.97,0:13:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kirin! Take Flora!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.64,0:13:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.39,0:13:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.69,0:13:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, Saya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.11,0:13:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Flora!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.95,0:13:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Toudou!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.33,0:13:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kirin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.25,0:13:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.17,0:14:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me.\NPlease take Flora!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.34,0:14:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L-Lady Toudou...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.30,0:14:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, go through that door.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.51,0:14:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.40,0:14:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So powerful!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.99,0:14:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.21,0:14:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kirin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.13,0:14:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kirin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.17,0:14:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move another muscle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.39,0:14:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's a vital spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.59,0:14:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't get it treated right away...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.60,0:14:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:14:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What can you do\Nin the shape you're in?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.36,0:15:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to test me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.87,0:15:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is that iai?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.67,0:15:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Toudou Style Art of Sword-drawing...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.14,0:15:38.23,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FOLDED WING
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.98,0:15:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Folded Wing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.23,0:15:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.23,0:15:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.36,0:15:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...\Na virtual image of a sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.62,0:16:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a great skill,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.71,0:16:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but not great enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.29,0:16:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.27,0:16:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kirin,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.68,0:16:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.98,0:16:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Toudou! Lady Toudou!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.27,0:16:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay? Lady Toudou!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.32,0:16:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please stay with us, Lady Toudou!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, right...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.40,0:16:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ayato-senpai and Julis-senpai's match...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.65,0:16:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How did it go, I wonder?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.21,0:16:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter with you,\NAyato Amagiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.14,0:16:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.68,0:16:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Burst into bloom...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.39,0:17:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Primrose!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.31,0:17:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously! What's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.86,0:17:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Any way you look at it,\Nhe's gotten way too powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.90,0:17:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously. I totally agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.24,0:17:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's on a whole different level\Nthan he was in the semifinals!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.07,0:17:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.32,0:17:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And he didn't throw up\Nmultiple protective walls, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.54,0:17:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am now able to master the use of this\Nsurging power far better than before!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.63,0:17:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How do I describe this joy?\NHow do I describe this thrill?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.89,0:17:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the true power\Nmy master granted me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.81,0:17:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,True power?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.44,0:17:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Julis...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.48,0:17:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What if this is AR-D at his\Nnormal specs right now... What then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.95,0:17:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You mean like your seal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.24,0:18:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not impossible,\Nbut why would he do such a...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.16,0:18:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then, let's see you take this hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.79,0:18:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is my...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.42,0:18:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.92,0:18:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wolnir Hammer!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.76,0:18:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Julis, hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.27,0:18:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he's upped\Nthe impact, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.86,0:18:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, we're not done yet\Nby a long shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.87,0:18:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And continuous fire, as well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.41,0:18:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Run, Julis!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.68,0:19:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then how do you like this method?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.76,0:19:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.60,0:19:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.85,0:19:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be dodging me\Nso easily now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.02,0:19:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wolnir Hammer...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.98,0:19:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fire!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.28,0:19:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Burst into bloom...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.82,0:19:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anthurium!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.83,0:19:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Julis...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.04,0:19:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.29,0:19:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.76,0:19:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you can stand\Neven after absorbing that direct hit...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.72,0:19:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just what I'd expect of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.47,0:19:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now that it's come to this,\Neven if we both go down...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.85,0:19:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How overwhelming is AR-D's power?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.57,0:20:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, looks like this\Nfinal match has been decided—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.66,0:20:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}H-H-Hold up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.87,0:20:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's going on? What's going on?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.83,0:20:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Uh... ahem.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Claudia?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.29,0:20:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato, Julis, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.84,0:20:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flora is safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.63,0:20:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And also...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.39,0:20:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.72,0:20:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.85,0:20:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then, pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.94,0:20:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That was Seidoukan Academy's\Nstudent council president just now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.95,0:20:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Uh, yeah... that was her...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.00,0:20:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, that girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.54,0:20:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how you look at it,\Nthat was going too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.21,0:20:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew she'd burst into that place\Njust to communicate with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.76,0:21:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since she's gone the extra mile\Nfor us, we can't lose now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.93,0:21:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For Saya and Kirin's sake, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.10,0:21:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what that was all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.14,0:21:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But all I can do is exert\Nmy power to the fullest!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.94,0:21:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wolnir Hammer!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.70,0:21:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's go, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.41,0:21:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ser=Versta!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.37,0:21:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fire!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.71,0:21:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.01,0:21:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.43,0:21:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now our counterattack begins!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.53,0:23:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Seriously, when you are with such a slow,\Nstupid good-for-nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.78,0:23:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}there's never enough time\Nto get anything done, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.12,0:23:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}All right, let me present\Nthe preview now while I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.66,0:23:39.96,Next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 21\NClinching Victory
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.08,0:23:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Just a moment, RM-C!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.41,0:23:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Such an important duty\Nshould be mine to—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.62,0:23:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}All right, next episode—
